text: Jamie Chung (born April 10, 1983) is an American actress and television personality. She first became famous during 2004 when she was on Real World on MTV. She played Claire in the movie Sorority Row. She plays Pam in the 2015 movie A Year and Change. Chung was born in San Francisco, California. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from San Francisco Category:1983 births Category:Living people
